00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:07,520
So we're already not really convinced of scientism.

118
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:09,880
But it doesn't mean that we have to talk about idealism.

119
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:12,240
But there's this little thing about,

